metadata.name: MY SUPER POWERS
metadata.description:
About my new collection...My SUPER POWERS. 
It all about my belief that every human on earth came to this world with a certain ability peculiar to only that person. That ability or strength is your super powers which are at different levels according to how much you know about it and are able to use it. Take for instance I was telling a pencil artist here how great his work is which I'm not well versed in as an artist...that is his super power. Some of us are good singers ,actors,scientists, leaders,listeners,nurtures...you name it. That is their super power. You super powers I believe is what comes naturally to you to do without being taught and you enjoy doing it and you are applauded or recognized for it.......
